description: Nio Strategic Metals Inc., a development stage company, engages in the exploration and development of mineral properties in the province of Quebec. The company explores for niobium and iron ores. It holds interest in the Oka mining property comprised of one mining lease and 102 claims covering an area of approximately 6,025 acres; and the Great Whale Iron property comprising 140 claims covering an area of approximately 17,098 acres located in the Hudson Bay territory. The company was formerly known as Niocan Inc. and changed its name to Nio Strategic Metals Inc. in June 2022. Nio Strategic Metals Inc. was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Montreal, Canada.
